                            <comment id="261080" author="adilger" created="Sat, 11 Jan 2020 02:51:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added Minh, since he was the author for that patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Elena, I don&apos;t mind to make this optional. It seems we could also specify it as part of &lt;tt&gt;$MPIRUN_OPITIONS&lt;/tt&gt; from the environment, but maybe this has some side-effect that I&apos;m not aware of?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="260100" author="egryaznova" created="Wed, 18 Dec 2019 14:18:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Andreas,&lt;br/&gt;
Jian,&lt;br/&gt;
we need your advice how to fix this. I see only the way to remove this option or make it optional.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please advice.&lt;br/&gt;
Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
